quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  12,103,"Ìwọ ìbáà ṣojú kòkòrò (ìgbàlà wọn), ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ ènìyàn ni kò níí gbàgbọ́."
  12,104,"Ìwọ kò sì bi wọ́n léèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan lórí rẹ̀. Kò sì jẹ́ kiní kan bí kò ṣe ìrántí fún gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  12,105,"Àti pé mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn àmì tí ń bẹ ní sánmọ̀ àti ní orí ilẹ̀ tí wọ́n ń ré kọjá lórí rẹ̀, tí wọ́n sì ń gbúnrí kúrò níbẹ̀."
  14,49,"O sì máa rí àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀ ní ọjọ́ yẹn, tí wọn yóò so wọ́n papọ̀ mọ́ra wọn sínú sẹ́kẹ́sẹkẹ̀."
  14,50,"Oje gbígbóná ni àwọn èwù wọn. Iná yó sì bo ojú wọn mọ́lẹ̀ bámúbámú"
  14,51,"nítorí kí Allāhu lè san ẹ̀san ohun tí ẹ̀mí kọ̀ọ̀kan ṣe níṣẹ́ fún un. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Olùyára níbi ìṣírò-iṣẹ́."
  15,22,"Àti pé A rán àwọn atẹ́gùn láti kó àwọn ẹ̀ṣújò jọ. A sì sọ omi kalẹ̀ láti sánmọ̀. Nítorí náà, A fún yín mu. Ẹ̀yin sì kọ́ ni ẹ kó omi òjò jọ (sójú sánmọ̀)."
  15,23,"Dájúdájú Àwa, Àwa ń sọ (ẹ̀dá) di alààyè. A sì ń sọ ọ́ di òkú. Àwa sì ni A óò jogún (ẹ̀dá)."
  15,24,"Àti pé dájúdájú A mọ àwọn olùgbawájú nínú yín. Dájúdájú A sì mọ àwọn olùgbẹ̀yìn."
  16,1,"Àṣẹ Allāhu dé tán. Ẹ ma wulẹ̀ wá a pẹ̀lú ìkánjú. Mímọ́ ni fún Un. Ó sì ga tayọ n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń fi ṣẹbọ sí I."
  16,2,"(Allāhu) ń fi àṣẹ Rẹ̀ sọ mọlāika (Jibrīl) kalẹ̀ láti máa mú ìmísí wá díẹ̀díẹ̀ fún ẹnikẹ́ni tí Ó bá fẹ́ (bẹ́ẹ̀ fún) nínú àwọn ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀ nítorí kí ẹ lè fi ṣe ìkìlọ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Èmi. Nítorí náà, ẹ bẹ̀rù Mi.”"
  16,3,"Ó ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ pẹ̀lú òdodo. Ó ga tayọ n̄ǹkan tí wọ́n ń fi ṣẹbọ sí I."